- Copy the JAR file from build/libs to your Minecraft mods folder (usually located in %APPDATA%\.minecraft\mods on Windows or ~/Library/Application Support/minecraft/mods on macOS).

Now, when you run Minecraft with the Forge profile, your jump height should be altered according to the value you set in the SuperJumpEventHandler class. Note that this example is for Minecraft 1.12.2, and you may need to make adjustments for other versions.

